-- Nordstrom Jan same-store sales fall 6.6 pct
-- 
-- Thu Feb 7, 2008 7:51am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/07/us-usa-retailsales-nordstrom-idUSWNAS986320080207

 

 ATLANTA  (Reuters) - Upscale department store chain Nordstrom Inc. ( JWN.N ) said on Thursday January sales at stores open at least a year fell 6.6 percent. 

 Analysts, on average, were expecting the company's same-store sales to fall 0.5 percent, according to Reuters Estimates. (Reporting by  Karen Jacobs ; Editing by  Derek Caney )